      - **Corrective Actions:** How any issues were addressed
    example_finding: **Finding:** All candidates (N=47) evaluated using same skill matrix derived from job requirements. No protected characteristics considered. Selection criteria applied consistently. No adverse impact detected (selection rate parity across available demographic data). All decisions documented with job-related rationale.
  eeo_1_support:
